    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and has been well-cared for over the years. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how well it handles. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
