      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a factory Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver\u2019s example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive Double VANOS refresh and rod bearing replacement with ACL shells. To address the chassis's inherent weak points, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with structural plates. Performance is enhanced by a bespoke suspension setup featuring Bilstein B16 adjustable coilovers and powerflex bushings for sharpened turn-in. The M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. While the Titan Silver finish displays minor road rash and the interior shows light bolster wear, the powertrain remains exceptionally healthy with strong compression across all cylinders. A visceral, analog experience for the discerning technician.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "2020 Sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor cosmetic wear. Reliable performance. Service records available.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
