    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of reliability and care, perfect for a driver who values both performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the hood reflect its honest miles on the road. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with plush upholstery that remains firm and supportive; the dashboard and controls show minimal wear, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is sound, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake service. It drives straight and true, with a smooth transmission and a responsive engine that still feels spirited. This is a well-maintained, dependable car that balances a clean aesthetic with a proven track record of longevity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
